                    <p>&emsp;&emsp;预付款￥：<span id="advanceChargeAmt"></span>元（大写）<span id="advanceChargeAmtB"></span></p>
                    <p id="saleType">&emsp;&emsp;银行按揭：审核贷款通过后，买方按购车计算表提车首付款金额（￥
